name: Three Legged Race Jewelry Holder (8 x 10)
description:
**This item is made to order. Pattern placement in fabric, and natural wood textures and colors in frame may vary from shown picture. Barnwood frames are rustic, and no two are exactly alike. Message me with any questions.**

Beautiful, rustic and distressed 8 x 10 frame (11 x 13 total outside measurements). This jewelry holder is perfect for anyone with a more natural, eco friendly, bohemian chic style.

The silver metal wire on top of the fabric offers flexible placing for all of your favorite earrings, no matter what size. There are SEVEN silver 1" hooks on the bottom of the frame to provide space to hang necklaces, bracelets, headbands, etc.

There are two sawtooth hooks on the back for steady and level mounting. This frame looks great in a bedroom, bathroom, or walk in closet!
